{"tid":502282,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人好鍾意睇人地食野既片？","createTime":"2017-12-17T17:32:38.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-18T06:53:42.000Z","uid":140094,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"80bba8cf9819b64071b9bb7c6835cda473fd4f3d","tid":502282,"uid":140094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T17:32:38.000Z","msg":"好鍾意係YouTube睇食野片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n本身好鍾意睇木下 但睇左同木下一齊拍節目既俄羅斯佐藤既片 就返唔到轉頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n木下可能因為要日日出片 而家有時食D野好劣 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  但佐藤食既同有時煮既野係靚好多同個樣好食好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n巨型蛋包飯<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/18/011719_2f7896e96eb526098f38110914e3f536.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F18%2F011719_2f7896e96eb526098f38110914e3f536.png&h=a9be049f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=NOWxM6KgzfM&amp;t=259s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DNOWxM6KgzfM%26t%3D259s&d=RXrr1d%2FdcN24KA%2FI9NaZ9U%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=96420038\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=NOWxM6KgzfM&amp;t=259s</a><br />\n<br />\n日式叉燒蛋飯<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/18/011857_c0cf7a16a49d56afe0192fa962549018.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F18%2F011857_c0cf7a16a49d56afe0192fa962549018.png&h=f81ec8f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=1060pmAT-H8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D1060pmAT-H8&d=RXrr1d%2FdcN24KA%2FI9NaZ9U%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=4cd1feff\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=1060pmAT-H8</a><br />\n<br />\n吞拿魚丼飯<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/18/012321_8ebbf2001d127c83a5c39e16f32189dd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F18%2F012321_8ebbf2001d127c83a5c39e16f32189dd.png&h=87257ff4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=hkjw1DQ9l80\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dhkjw1DQ9l80&d=RXrr1d%2FdcN24KA%2FI9NaZ9U%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=44117840\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=hkjw1DQ9l80</a><br />\n<br />\n聖誕大餐<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/18/012514_fabe088fa10210d872b105bbb1bb017f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F18%2F012514_fabe088fa10210d872b105bbb1bb017f.png&h=ad0a3cd7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=P92Sq3kjDjs&amp;t=16s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DP92Sq3kjDjs%26t%3D16s&d=RXrr1d%2FdcN24KA%2FI9NaZ9U%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=ea4f8f12\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=P92Sq3kjDjs&amp;t=16s</a><br />\n<br />\n另外呢個谷崎鷹人 /谷やん 都係煮D野好好食咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n南蠻炸雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/18/012831_e435d4fe96a4c24bfcb8a22b7e109fec.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%